: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">• To make our education accessible to all sections of the community.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">• To strive to inculcate a spirit of temperance, tolerance and charity in each child.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">• To promote justice, religious and cultural pluralism, thus transcending boundaries of caste, creed and community.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">• To promote love for the arts and our national heritage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">• To make our school a centre of human, spiritual, cultural and academic formation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">• To build boys and girls of strength and character – with the courage of their convictions so that each individual becomes the person he/she is meant to be – a full and effective human being in heart, mind and spirit.</p>\r\n</div>','',-2,84,'2018-08-22 09:48:27',313,'','2018-08-22 09:48:27',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2018-08-22 09:48:27','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\