p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Objectives :<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To focus on individual development, a sense of discipline and an appreciation of the highest ideals of character of each child.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To inculcate a sense of values and love for any task in each child, thereby laying the foundation of control over his\\/her own life and destiny.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To make our school a centre of human, spiritual, cultural and academic excellence.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To make our education accessible to all sections of the community.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To strive to inculcate a spirit of temperance, tolerance and charity in each child.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To promote justice, religious and cultural pluralism, thus transcending boundaries of caste, creed and community.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To promote love for the arts and our national heritage.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To make our school a centre of human, spiritual, cultural and academic formation.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">\\u2022 To build boys and girls of strength and character \\u2013 with the courage of their convictions so that each individual becomes the person he\\/she is meant to be \\u2013 a full and effective human being in heart, mind and spirit.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"84\",\"created\":\"2018-08-22 09:48:27\",\"created_by\":\"313\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-08-22 09:48:27\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2018-08-22 09:48:27\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"url